  "labelDisableContentFeatures": "Disable Content Features",
  "tooltipDisableContentFeatures": "Master switch for all content-layer features. When on, NAMS runs as a pure engine layer (mouse fixes, validation, heap tuning, crash fixes) without any item / weapon / outfit / quest / accessory mod support. Useful for benchmarking or isolating engine vs content issues.",
  "labelContentItems": "Items / Weapons / Shops",
  "tooltipContentItems": "Custom items, weapons, outfits and shop entries. Disable to play without any item-related mods. Requires restart.",
